stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Bootstrap: first boot

    state Bootstrap {
        direction TB
        RepoSeed: Repo Seed\n(shell plugins as npm deps)
        ExplicitPlugins: Explicit plugin URLs\n+ SHA-256 hardcoded
        EmptyOPFS: OPFS empty\n(no user graph yet)

        RepoSeed --> ExplicitPlugins
        ExplicitPlugins --> EmptyOPFS
    }

    Bootstrap --> Inflexion: first refarm:PluginRegistry\nnode confirmed in OPFS

    state Inflexion {
        direction TB
        note: Tractor sync writes\nPluginRegistry node → OPFS.\nDistro detects it and shifts\nto graph-driven config.
    }

    Inflexion --> Sovereign: graph-driven mode active

    state Sovereign {
        direction TB
        GraphDiscovery: Plugin discovery\nvia refarm:PluginRegistry
        GraphConfig: Distro config\nread from graph
        FullOPFS: OPFS has user's\ncomplete sovereign graph

        GraphDiscovery --> GraphConfig
        GraphConfig --> FullOPFS
    }

    Sovereign --> [*]: user can export, fork or migrate

    note right of Bootstrap: Everything comes from the repo.\nTractor syncs an empty graph.
    note right of Sovereign: Shell plugins (Herald, Firefly)\nstill come from repo.\nContent plugins + config\ncome from the graph.
